title: Add the location -120,-43 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0xbf38f4174b1e86fb6baac287209bbc7b0524f9d9 (BEATKOIN)

## BAYLANDO - CUMBIA TOWN

![BAYLANDO - CUMBIA TOWN](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/-120/-43/map.png)

Should the scene located at -120,-43 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

The Scene at -120,-43 Titled "Cumbia Town" is the first latin music club in Decentraland it's also a real party in Oakland & The most popular Cumbia party in the Bay Area, I am trying to integrate the two worlds and promote Decentraland to my Fans

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=9d5cb510-3a86-11ec-be0c-afec86cba5e5)**
author: 0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958
